= Limitations of the Study
<limitations-of-the-study>
== Sample Size Constraints
<sample-size-constraints>
While the effect size was statistically significant (#mi(`p < 0.01`)),
the limited cohort size (#mi(`N=45`)) restricts the generalizability of
our findings across diverse demographic populations.

== Measurement Artifacts
<measurement-artifacts>
Signal attenuation in the fiber optic relay introduced minor, albeit
non-negligible, baseline drift during the prolonged observation windows.
